tag jj|||Shoot your way through the worlds only zombie prison. No one will let you leave. Jump, run, swim, and tear your way passed hordes of undead. It only gets worse from here.  Researchers have opened the holes to hell... There is no stopping the dead from rising out. The world organizations have turned the site into a fortified stronghold to keep the dead from escaping. But the local government has turned it into a prison. You have been convicted of a crime of racketeering and attempted coup, you are now thrown behind the thick walls. Your only escape is to go into the pit and attempt to get out alive.
